you’ll need to disable your NAT and have permission to bridge your modem to the router (if not done already)

item.title: [PI] Client help
item.dc:creator: @Liquid_Magic Liquid Magic
item.description:
@Liquid_Magic wrote:

sorry I took so long I was helping someone else and I had to edit my environmental variables because of the new JDK update

it’d be something like this:

@echo off
cd src dir
javac *.java -cp . -d ../class dir/
pause

what that does it compile everything in your src bin, and move the class files to your classpath which in your case is “Class” i assume
